00:24:14,458 --> 00:24:16,416
醒來，想起了她來這裡的目的。
woken up and remembered what she's here for.

351
00:24:16,460 --> 00:24:18,244
[公告繼續模糊]
[announcement continues indistinctly]

352
00:24:30,125 --> 00:24:32,301
嗯……[嘆氣]
Well... [sighs]

353
00:24:32,345 --> 00:24:34,390
向你致敬，女孩。
Hats off to you, girl.

354
00:24:34,434 --> 00:24:36,218
你去爭取了。
You went for it.

355
00:24:37,481 --> 00:24:39,221
我會去找聖約翰救護車。
I'll go find a St John's Ambulance.

356
00:24:39,265 --> 00:24:41,049
他們可能有很多白蘭地。
They might have a tot of brandy.

357
00:24:42,268 --> 00:24:43,791
為了我。
For me.

358
00:24:43,835 --> 00:24:46,402
你是對的，Vi——所有的錢。
You were right, Vi-- all that money.

359
00:24:47,752 --> 00:24:49,841
我的埃迪會為我感到羞恥的。
My Eddie'd be ashamed of me.

360
00:24:51,233 --> 00:24:53,148
我馬上回來，嗯？
I'll be right back, huh?

361
00:24:57,849 --> 00:25:01,069
做夢沒什麼錯，艾達，嗯？
Nothing wrong with dreaming, Ada, hmm?

362
00:25:01,113 --> 00:25:03,115
當我來到倫敦時，
When I came to London,

363
00:25:03,158 --> 00:25:05,334
街道上鋪滿了我的夢想。
the streets were paved with my dreams.

364
00:25:11,079 --> 00:25:13,560
[嘆氣]這就是你。
[sighs] That's what you are.

365
00:25:13,604 --> 00:25:15,736
你是個夢想家。
You're a dreamer.

366
00:25:15,780 --> 00:25:17,825
就像你臉上的鼻子一樣平淡。
Plain as the nose on your face.

367
00:25:19,784 --> 00:25:21,481
[輕彈]
[lighter flicks]

368
00:25:44,939 --> 00:25:46,593
[敲門聲]
[knocking]

369
00:25:49,378 --> 00:25:51,076
[敲門聲]
[knocking]

370
00:25:52,251 --> 00:25:55,820
放棄吧，維。我很好。
Give over, Vi. I'm all right.

371
00:25:55,863 --> 00:25:57,604
男：哈里斯夫人？
MAN: Mrs. Harris?

372
00:25:57,648 --> 00:25:59,693
愛德華·哈里斯夫人？
Mrs. Edward Harris?

373
00:25:59,737 --> 00:26:01,565
是關於你丈夫的。
It's about your husband.

374
00:26:03,392 --> 00:26:05,569
艾達：請坐。
ADA: Sit down, please.

375
00:26:06,744 --> 00:26:09,398
哈里斯中士並未在行動中被宣布失?
Sergeant Harris wasn't declared missing in action

376
00:26:09,442 --> 00:26:11,139
直到4月19日。
until April the 19th.

377
00:26:11,183 --> 00:26:13,272
嗯，是的，那是我收到電報的時候。
Uh, yeah, that's when I got the telegram.

378
00:26:13,315 --> 00:26:15,404
這是他生日的第二天。
It's a day after his birthday.

379
00:26:15,448 --> 00:26:17,624
是的。
Ah, yes.

380
00:26:17,668 --> 00:26:20,888
嗯，我們現在知道，
Well, um, as we now know,

381
00:26:20,932 --> 00:26:25,719
1944 年 3 月 2 日，Polo Lima 326 航班墜毀，
Flight Polo Lima 326 crashed on March the 2nd, 1944,

382
00:26:25,763 --> 00:26:28,026
意味著哈里斯中士得到了報酬
meaning that Sergeant Harris was paid

383
00:26:28,069 --> 00:26:31,029
在他死後將近七個星期。
for almost seven weeks after his death.

384
00:26:32,117 --> 00:26:35,642
在，嗯，每天六先令。
At, um, six shillings a day.

385
00:26:35,686 --> 00:26:38,297
你是來告訴我的嗎？
Is that what you come to tell me?

386
00:26:38,340 --> 00:26:40,473
畢竟這段時間。
After all this time.

387
00:26:41,605 --> 00:26:43,302
我的埃迪欠你的錢？
That my Eddie owes you back pay?

388
00:26:43,345 --> 00:26:45,391
當他一生中從未欠過一分錢時e.
When he never owed a penny in his life.

389
00:26:45,434 --> 00:26:47,741
當他為國王和國家放棄生命時。
When he give up his life for king and country.

390
00:26:47,785 --> 00:26:49,395
你有神經。
You got a nerve.

391
00:26:49,438 --> 00:26:51,092
來到我家，喝我的茶，
Coming into my home, drinking my tea,

392
00:26:51,136 --> 00:26:52,398
抹黑他的名字。
blackening his name.

393
00:26:52,441 --> 00:26:54,661
-嗯... -你想要多少？
-Um... -How much do you want?

394
00:26:54,705 --> 00:26:56,402
多少錢？然後你就可以離開了。
How much? And then you can leave.

395
00:26:56,445 --> 00:26:58,056
我-我認為你搞錯了。
I-I think you've got the wrong end of the stick.

396
00:26:58,099 --> 00:26:59,579
哦，我有嗎？好吧，我會告訴你
Oh, have I? Well, I'll tell you

397
00:26:59,623 --> 00:27:01,189
你可以在一分鐘內把你的棍子推到哪裡，
where you can shove your stick in a minute,

398
00:27:01,233 --> 00:27:03,148
- 如果你不小心。 -哦，天哪，不。嗯，我，呃……
-if you don't watch out. -Oh, golly, no. Um, I, uh...

399
00:27:03,191 --> 00:27:04,845
我是來給你錢的 哈里斯夫人
I'm here to give you money, Mrs. Harris,

400
00:27:04,889 --> 00:27:07,369
-不-不從你那裡拿走它。 -我受夠了...
-not-not to take it from you. -I've had enough of...

401
00:27:07,413 --> 00:27:08,980
你說什麼？
What'd you say?

402
00:27:09,023 --> 00:27:11,286
是的。對。
Y-Yes. Righto.

403
00:27:11,330 --> 00:27:13,288
呃，你應該收到
Uh, you should have been receiving

404
00:27:13,332 --> 00:27:16,727
a-自 1944 年以來的戰爭寡婦撫卹金。
a-a war widow's pension since 1944.

405
00:27:16,770 --> 00:27:20,252
額，額，額，扣除這麼少。
It comes to quite a tidy sum, uh, with that small deduction.

406
00:27:21,296 --> 00:27:23,342
只要你沒有再婚。
So long as you haven't remarried.

407
00:27:23,385 --> 00:27:25,170
哦，放棄吧。
Oh, give over.

408
00:27:25,213 --> 00:27:26,911
他可能隨時會回來，
He might have come back any minute,

409
00:27:26,954 --> 00:27:28,477
我會看起來是正確的查理。
I'd have looked a right Charlie.

410
00:27:28,521 --> 00:27:31,132
-[輕笑] -呃...
-[chuckles] -Uh...

411
00:27:31,176 --> 00:27:32,830
出色地...
well...

412
00:27:32,873 --> 00:27:34,832
[硬幣在桌子上叮噹作響]
[coins clink on table]

413
00:27:34,875 --> 00:27:37,486
我想你最好坐下。
I suppose you'd better sit down.

414
00:27:38,531 --> 00:27:40,446
畢竟喝了那杯茶。
Have that cup of tea after all.

415
00:27:40,489 --> 00:27:42,753
嗯，沒有牛奶。
Um, no milk.

416
00:27:42,796 --> 00:27:45,712
VI：她這輩子從來沒有做錯任何事，先生。
VI: She's never done a thing wrong her whole life, sir.

417
00:27:45,756 --> 00:27:48,019
她因為一件衣服有點發瘋，
She went a bit crazy on account of some dress,

418
00:27:48,062 --> 00:27:50,412
但她現在很好。
but she's fine now.

419
00:27:50,456 --> 00:27:52,327
警察：沒什麼好擔心的。
POLICEMAN: Nothing to worry about.

420
00:27:57,593 --> 00:27:59,639
-ADA：哦，你好。 -太太。哈里斯？
-ADA: Oh, hello. -Mrs. Harris?

421
00:27:59,683 --> 00:28:01,641
你來告訴我我得到了皇冠上的珠寶？
You come to tell me I got the crown jewels?

422
00:28:01,685 --> 00:28:03,121
她的頭腦仍然不正確。
She's still not right in the head.

423
00:28:03,164 --> 00:28:05,645
幾乎。你遞過來的那個鑽石夾——
Almost. That diamond clip you handed in--

424
00:28:05,689 --> 00:28:07,691
主人想給你獎勵
the owner wants to give you a reward

425
00:28:07,734 --> 00:28:09,693
——作為一個誠實的公民。 -[笑]
-for being an honest citizen. -[laughs]

426
00:28:09,736 --> 00:28:12,913
哦！先生，她是誠實的。
Oh! She is, sir, honest to a fault.

427
00:28:12,957 --> 00:28:14,654
進來喝杯茶。
Come in and have a cup of tea.

428
00:28:14,698 --> 00:28:16,177
不要介意我這樣做。謝謝你。
Don't mind if I do. Thank you.

429
00:28:16,221 --> 00:28:17,744
哦，來吧，維。我們可以單膝跪地。
Oh, come on, Vi. We can have a knees-up.

430
00:28:17,788 --> 00:28:19,311
阿奇：餵，等我一下。
ARCHIE: Oi, wait for me.

431
00:28:19,354 --> 00:28:21,705
而且，呃，你可能想打破泡沫。
And, uh, you might want to break out the bubbly.

432
00:28:21,748 --> 00:28:23,489
你還有幸運的一天嗎，阿奇？
You having another lucky day, Archie?

433
00:28:23,532 --> 00:28:25,447
事實上，我是，你也是。
As a matter of fact, I am, and so are you.

434
00:28:25,491 --> 00:28:27,275
消息傳得很快。
News travels fast.

435
00:28:27,319 --> 00:28:29,756
所以，你賭那條兩條腿的狗……
So, that bet you put on that two-legged dog...

436
00:28:29,800 --> 00:28:31,758
哦，是的，別……別擔心。
Oh, y-yeah, don't... don't worry about that.

437
00:28:31,802 --> 00:28:33,325
我已經清醒過來了。
I've come to me senses.

438
00:28:33,368 --> 00:28:34,935
[笑]：不，老闆在那裡，
[chuckles]: No, the boss was there,

439
00:28:34,979 --> 00:28:36,458
所以我不得不拿錢，
so I had to take the money,

440
00:28:36,502 --> 00:28:38,373
但我設法忍住了。
but I managed to hold back a tenner.

441
00:28:38,417 --> 00:28:40,332
你不應該那樣做，阿奇。
You shouldn't have done that, Archie.

442
00:28:40,375 --> 00:28:41,855
你可能遇到了麻煩。
You could have got into trouble.

443
00:28:41,899 --> 00:28:43,509
所有的票噓聲，哈里斯夫人？
All tickety-boo, Mrs. Harris?

444
00:28:44,815 --> 00:28:46,904
哦，對不起，我不知道你有公司。
Oh, sorry, I didn't realize you had company.

445
00:28:46,947 --> 00:28:49,254
你好。這裡發生了什麼？
Hello. What's going on here?

446
00:28:49,297 --> 00:28:50,908
-ADA：哦。 - 為了邁克的愛。
-ADA: Oh. -For the love of Mike.

447
00:28:50,951 --> 00:28:53,214
——嗯，待會見。 -ADA：呃，不，阿奇，阿奇。
-Uh, I'll see you later. -ADA: Uh, no, Archie, Archie.

448
00:28:53,258 --> 00:28:54,868
呃，你能給我一點時間嗎？
Uh, can you just give me a moment?

449
00:28:54,912 --> 00:28:56,652
-它-這是個人的。 -[Vi 口哨]
-It-it's personal. -[Vi whistles]

450
00:28:56,696 --> 00:28:58,567
- 水壺在召喚？ -啊，沒錯。
-That the kettle calling? -Ah, righto.

451
00:28:59,525 --> 00:29:00,744
[門關閉]
[door closes]

452
00:29:00,787 --> 00:29:02,571
這是怎麼回事？有事嗎？
What's going on? Something up?

453
00:29:02,615 --> 00:29:03,834
說來話長。
It's a long story.

454
00:29:03,877 --> 00:29:05,139
你在說什麼？
What were you saying?

455
00:29:05,183 --> 00:29:06,793
所以，我拿了你的錢
So, I took your money

456
00:29:06,837 --> 00:29:09,013
並在最後一場比賽中確定無疑。
and put it on a sure thing in the last race.

457
00:29:09,056 --> 00:29:11,276
還有，嗯...
And, um...

458
00:29:12,277 --> 00:29:14,627
......你的股份回來了，還有一點點。
...your stake back and a wee bit more.

459
00:29:16,194 --> 00:29:18,500
哦，不，不，阿奇，我不能。
Oh, n-no, Archie, I couldn't.

460
00:29:18,544 --> 00:29:21,199
-我... -這是你的錢。拿著。
-I... -It's your money. Take it.

461
00:29:21,242 --> 00:29:22,896
養不下去了嗚嗚男人。
I can't keep it, woman.

462
00:29:22,940 --> 00:29:25,072
那裡的 PC Plod 會有我的許可證。來吧。
PC Plod in there would have my license. Come on.

463
00:29:26,073 --> 00:29:28,684
[笑]
[laughing]

464
00:29:28,728 --> 00:29:31,035
只要答應我在軍團跳舞。
Just promise me a dance at the Legion.

465
00:29:34,603 --> 00:29:36,649
謝謝，阿奇。
Thanks, Archie.

466
00:29:36,692 --> 00:29:38,216
非常感謝。
Much obliged.

467
00:29:43,438 --> 00:29:44,613
天哪。
Blimey.

468
00:29:44,657 --> 00:29:46,137
[輕笑]
[chuckles]

469
00:29:58,889 --> 00:30:00,891
[飛機嘎嘎作響]
[plane rattling]

470
00:30:03,415 --> 00:30:04,982
我們在飛嗎？
Are we flying?

471
00:30:05,025 --> 00:30:06,374
[對講鈴聲]
[intercom chimes]

472
00:30:06,418 --> 00:30:07,593
乘務員：我們非常抱歉，
FLIGHT ATTENDANT: We're terribly sorry,

473
00:30:07,636 --> 00:30:08,899
女士們先生們。
ladies and gentlemen.

474
00:30:08,942 --> 00:30:10,944
似乎一台發動機有故障。
There seems to be a fault with one engine.

475
00:30:10,988 --> 00:30:12,467
會有輕微延遲
There will be a slight delay

476
00:30:12,511 --> 00:30:14,513
當我們嘗試解決問題時。
while we try and fix the problem.

477
00:30:14,556 --> 00:30:16,254
延遲？
Delay?

478
00:30:16,297 --> 00:30:18,038
多久？
How long?

479
00:30:19,300 --> 00:30:21,650
我必須在一天之內到達那裡並回來。
I've got to be there and back in a day.

480
00:30:33,706 --> 00:30:35,316
[輕輕打鼾]
[snores softly]

481
00:30:35,360 --> 00:30:37,492
[喘氣，耳語]：哦，上帝。
[gasps, whispers]: Oh, God.

482
00:30:41,801 --> 00:30:43,194
[喘氣]
[gasps]

483
00:30:43,237 --> 00:30:44,586
巴黎。
Paris.

484
00:31:00,515 --> 00:31:02,561
-[模糊的喋喋不休] -[按喇叭]
-[indistinct chatter] -[horn honks]

485
00:31:10,221 --> 00:31:12,571
Righto，巴黎，我來了。
Righto, Paris, here I come.

486
00:31:16,923 --> 00:31:19,012
這是一個相當古老的步行。
It's a fair old walk.

487
00:31:22,059 --> 00:31:24,104
[交通隆隆聲]
[traffic rumbling]

488
00:31:37,770 --> 00:31:39,685
-[男人咳嗽] -[Ada 吸鼻子]
-[man coughs] -[Ada sniffs]

489
00:31:39,728 --> 00:31:41,339
【火車汽笛聲】
[train whistle blows]

490
00:31:41,382 --> 00:31:43,471
[P.A. 的法語公告]
[announcement in French over P.A.]

491
00:31:47,998 --> 00:31:50,174
哦。嗯...
Oh. Um...

492
00:31:50,217 --> 00:31:51,697
你好。
bonjour.

493
00:31:53,220 --> 00:31:54,830
請問你說什麼？
Beg your pardon?

494
00:31:54,874 --> 00:31:56,006
[笑]
[laughs]

495
00:31:57,572 --> 00:31:58,834
[男人笑]
[men laughing]

496
00:31:58,878 --> 00:32:00,358
嘿。
Hey.

497
00:32:01,881 --> 00:32:04,057
艾達：謝謝。是的。
ADA: Thank you. Yeah.

498
00:32:06,668 --> 00:32:10,411
嗯，我是來買衣服的。
Um, I'm here to buy a dress.

499
00:32:10,455 --> 00:32:11,673
來自迪奧。
From Dior.

500
00:32:11,717 --> 00:32:13,240
-迪奧？ -[都在喃喃自語]
-Dior? -[all muttering]

501
00:32:13,284 --> 00:32:15,547
啊，oui.Me也是。
Ah, oui.Me also.

502
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:17,984
[笑聲]
[laughter]

503
00:32:19,464 --> 00:32:21,814
遠嗎——迪奧？
Is it far-- Dior?

504
00:32:21,857 --> 00:32:23,337
哦……[嘆氣]
Oh... [sighs]

505
00:32:23,381 --> 00:32:25,296
20分鐘。
20 minutes.

506
00:32:25,339 --> 00:32:28,125
呃，但是在你喝酒之後，兩個小時。
Uh, but after you take wine, two hours.

507
00:32:28,168 --> 00:32:30,344
[笑聲]
[laughter]

508
00:32:31,693 --> 00:32:33,173
我帶你去那裡。
I walk you there.

509
00:32:33,217 --> 00:32:34,392
[打嗝]
[burps]

510
00:32:34,435 --> 00:32:36,916
明天早上，嗯？
Tomorrow morning, eh?

511
00:32:40,528 --> 00:32:41,529
哦，不，不，謝謝。
Oh, no, no, thanks.

512
00:32:41,573 --> 00:32:43,531
我不能，不。
I couldn't, no.

513
00:32:44,532 --> 00:32:45,490
[咕嚕聲]
[grunts]

514
00:32:45,533 --> 00:32:46,665
[輕笑]
[chuckles]

515
00:32:46,708 --> 00:32:48,058
[男人笑]
[men laughing]

516
00:32:48,101 --> 00:32:50,364
好吧，那就繼續吧。 [笑]
All right, go on, then. [laughs]

517
00:32:56,327 --> 00:32:57,937
哦，天哪。 [笑]
Oh, blimey. [laughs]

518
00:32:57,981 --> 00:33:00,070
[笑聲]
[laughter]

519
00:33:14,432 --> 00:33:17,043
ADA：為什麼街上到處都是垃圾？
ADA: Why is all this rubbish on the streets?

520
00:33:17,087 --> 00:33:18,784
米歇爾：大老闆出軌了……
MICHEL: The big boss cheats...

521
00:33:18,827 --> 00:33:20,090
[說法語]
[speaks French]

522
00:33:20,133 --> 00:33:21,830
- 工人，是嗎？ -是啊。
-The worker, yes? -Yeah, yeah.

523
00:33:24,398 --> 00:33:25,834
工人說：“沒有了。”
The worker say, "No more."

524
00:33:28,098 --> 00:33:29,621
賓門罷工了？
The binmen are on strike?

525
00:33:29,664 --> 00:33:31,623
是的。
Ah, yes.

526
00:33:31,666 --> 00:33:33,755
